Psuedocode for creating mario pyramid by taking dimension from user

1. Get A Positive Number From user between 1 and 8 including . this will be height of our pyramid.
2. First we will print hashes by making a for loop and print them in ascending order top to bottom  from left to right.
3  make a formula that will determine number of hashes & dots in a paricular line just from height number.
4. Then we will add dots from left to right on blank spaces to indent hashes in desired way.
5. now we will remove the dots to blank spaces to get desired result.